  <body>
    <segment id="1" parent="11" relname="joint">1) The challenge facing World Wildlife Fund is global.</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="11" relname="joint">
2) And time is running out.</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="16" relname="span">
3) We need your member-ship support now.</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="12" relname="span">
4) Extinction can come quickly.</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="4" relname="interpretation">
5) And extinction is forever.</segment>
    <segment id="6" parent="17" relname="span">
6) So please consider sending a member-ship contribu-tion of $15, $25, $50. or more if at all possible.</segment>
    <segment id="7" parent="13" relname="span">
7) As I said in the beginning of this letter. talk alone won&apos;t accomplish
much.</segment>
    <segment id="8" parent="7" relname="interpretation">
8) You and I both know that.</segment>
    <segment id="9" parent="14" relname="span">
9) It takes action to get the job done.</segment>
    <segment id="10" parent="15" relname="span">
10) I urge you to act today.</segment>
<group id="11" type="multinuc" parent="3" relname="volitional-cause" />
